# zloka_mudra.adesha — seal BG 2.47 (Harvard-Kyoto) with A0S fingerprint
# karmaṇy evādhikāras te mā phaleṣu kadācana |
# mā karma-phala-hetur bhūr mā te saṅgo 'stv akarmaṇi || (BG 2.47)
sthApaya zloka karmaNy evAdhikAras te mA phaleSu kadAcana | mA karma-phala-hetur bhUr mA te saMgo 'stv akarmaNi
vada zloka
mudrA zloka
